actions.text: Referred to House Committee on the District of Columbia.

official_title: A bill to retrocede a portion of the District of Columbia to the State of Maryland.

summary.text: Retrocedes and relinquishes a specified portion of the District of Columbia to the State of Maryland. Entitles the State of Maryland to one additional prepresentative for this area until the next apportionment.

titles.title: A bill to retrocede a portion of the District of Columbia to the State of Maryland.
